-05-24T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你自己冇時間學 關人咩事<br />\n同埋係人地預咗個期俾你 你唔要車"},{"pid":"320578db374225a941a3237a5ee84379b430e73c","tid":1168620,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"邊有人第一堂就比埋考試租車錢"},{"pid":"56bc0fb4f1e6bd246a13c87f60a0c6143015182d","tid":1168620,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"128b61feedd9d075c456932b2e8ed2a17a028f26","tid":1168620,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e83e2b7c5a4caaa40a13d113aa115f61f014637","tid":1168620,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"諗諗下都唔知佢係咪明知教唔晒<br />\n水我教試租車錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你自己冇時間學 關人咩事<br />\n同埋係人地預咗個期俾你 你唔要車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"我學之前有問佢 得番一個月學唔學得晒嘅就<br />\n同埋 成個5月 我真係日日得閒<br />\n只係佢比唔倒咁多日我學"},{"pid":"b39d3be53e78f4dfb1f786e31fdf8b2d0859caf9","tid":1168620,"uid":89801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"拎就拎得返 不過拎唔足<br />\n例如你之前學車 每堂250蚊 呢個價錢係你跟佢考試先offer比你<br />\n你宜家唔跟佢考試 收返你正價300蚊<br />\n你上左5日 10堂 即係要比返500蚊<br />\n你預繳左1800蚊考試費<br />\n佢咪退返1300蚊比你"}]}